optimize (1.0.8-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Suppress dpkg-query errors and implement fallbacks (linux-image, apt-cache, linux)
    for better kernel source package resolution
  * Improve .config detection (checks /boot, /proc/config.gz, falls back to defconfig)
  * Enhance kernel build process resilience by properly handling non-fatal errors
  * Add automatic dependency resolution with apt-get build-dep

