optimize (1.0.6-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Update installation method to use dpkg --force-overwrite and
    automatically fix broken dependencies.
  * Implement --kernel optimization flag using localmodconfig and
    KCFLAGS
  * Update README to document the --kernel parameter
  * Fix --kernel source package detection by querying linux-headers
    instead of linux-image
  * Fix make localmodconfig pipefail crash
  * Fix kernel build: Add libdw-dev dependency and use --set-str for
    trust keys

